{"tid":1865192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門管治衰過清朝 今日港共政府衰過咩朝代？","createTime":"2020-02-06T05:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T00:49:19.000Z","uid":101392,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"60390efa99c05a0bcda20cfc6152f7baf6704103","tid":1865192,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePbE9FZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePbE9FZ.jpg&h=cab419a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGx1Dzj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGx1Dzj.jpg&h=b5006af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPGUYzk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPGUYzk.jpg&h=a879213f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYeSLeq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYeSLeq.jpg&h=5f8f502a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解咁多人會咁在意港共政府俾澳門賀一誠大炒50:0<br />\n我諗係因為澳門政府嘅廢柴形象已經喺我哋心目中根深蒂固<br />\n打風搞到雞毛鴨血之餘<br />\n仲有東方一系列澳門政府「衰過清朝」報導 <br />\n諗到「衰過清朝」嚟形容嘅編輯真係犀利，一來，年代久遠，可以比喻倒退一百年，二來，晚清應該係最受列強欺侮、民族尊嚴最低落、最亂象頻生嘅時侯<br />\n<br />\n今日港共衰到咁 唔封關搞到醫護罷工、引中國人入關令社區爆發、不作為令市民搶口罩、搶糧食、搶廁紙<br />\n仲可以用咩朝代嚟形容？"},{"pid":"0225c37e883025cee1abbc027f822491716b1241","tid":1865192,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"衰過共朝三年大饑荒？"},{"pid":"32c64981c007da370d4ab0302421b7f6928b77aa","tid":1865192,"uid":101392,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"直接用「衰過澳門」已經係最大諷刺<br />\n比一個衰過清朝嘅政府更衰"},{"pid":"2528007ccc05bd812c9d34c201fba0ddbdcd1c37","tid":1865192,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0225c37e883025cee1abbc027f822491716b1241","tid":1865192,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"衰過共朝三年大饑荒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20